Hi, yes I solved my problem but it was a long time ago. I dug into the exceljs code and found an example. however now I don't remember which file it was. I can provide you my own code as an example.

const workbook = new ExcelJS.Workbook();
const workSheet = workbook.addWorksheet("TestSheet");

workSheet.addConditionalFormatting({
  ref: "A1:C1",
  rules: [
    {
      type: "dataBar",
      color: { argb: "85de71" },
      gradient: false,
      cfvo: [
        { type: "num", value: 0 },
        { type: "num", value: 1 }
      ]
    }
  ]
});
